{"tid":1693822,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想開始學琴 JJ插地求解答","createTime":"2019-11-04T23:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T01:16:25.000Z","uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04b07005c3f41e67a3da23329c6696612d33c1c4","tid":1693822,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:32:33.000Z","msg":"早五六年有學過一兩個月 跟琴行<br />\n但因為屋企冇琴 成日要出去練覺得好麻煩 所以就放棄咗<br />\n而家想學返 想問初學跟琴行定私人好?<br />\n私人既話要點搵老師 我住得好偏僻 想搵返同區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外就係今次學想買返部琴 但鋼琴又好撚貴<br />\n所以就諗住買二手鋼琴/數碼鋼琴<br />\n有冇巴打講下邊隻好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者有冇巴打屋企有琴唔要可以平讓俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申唔使彈到好勁唔使考級 想彈下流行歌或者成日都會聽到既古典音樂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34617b35b20ad6c5efac6a63bb188e2f9a5f189a","tid":1693822,"uid":15636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:40:20.000Z","msg":"彈到成日聽到既古典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5db969a13135f6445d30572c413964ef459948","tid":1693822,"uid":260390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04b07005c3f41e67a3da23329c6696612d33c1c4","tid":1693822,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:32:33.000Z","msg":"早五六年有學過一兩個月 跟琴行<br />\n但因為屋企冇琴 成日要出去練覺得好麻煩 所以就放棄咗<br />\n而家想學返 想問初學跟琴行定私人好?<br />\n私人既話要點搵老師 我住得好偏僻 想搵返同區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外就係今次學想買返部琴 但鋼琴又好撚貴<br />\n所以就諗住買二手鋼琴/數碼鋼琴<br />\n有冇巴打講下邊隻好<